OL,3,CPSNI chief vows to hunt down those
OL,4,Cbehind racist crimes
OL,6,FThe number of race hate incidents in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland is believed to have
OL,8,Frisen by a third, according to
OL,9,Fprovisional police numbers.
OL,11,FAn additional 409 incidents are
OL,12,Fthought to have taken place between
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 and September 2024 on
OL,14,Fthe basis of operational figures from
OL,15,Fthe Police Service of Northern Ireland.
