OL,4,Cbehind racist crimes
OL,6,FPolice in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Finvestigating the disorder have made
OL,8,F45 arrests so far and 35 people have
OL,9,Fbeen charged.
OL,11,FThe arrest total includes seven under
OL,12,Fthe age of 18, with the youngest just
OL,13,F11 years old.
OL,15,FAssistant Chief Constable Bobby
OL,16,FSingleton has issued a fresh appeal
OL,17,Ffor witnesses to come forward,
OL,18,Fhighlighting the anonymous
OL,19,FCrimestoppers charity for those who
OL,20,Fmay feel afraid to report.
